descript.abstract: World Time Zones (layer) is a symbolized and labeled display presentation of the World time zones data set. The geographic and attribute data World time zones are symbolized and labeled to create the layer. All features are symbolized as a single symbol. Features are labeled based on the ZONE attribute.
descript.supplinf: For more information about the data set, see its metadata.
